Gazit-Globe Increases Most in a Week as Leader Raises to ‘Buy’

-- B y   S h o s h a n n a   S o l o m o n
-- 
2011-09-18T14:14:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-18/gazit-globe-increases-most-in-a-week-as-leader-raises-to-buy-.html
Gazit-Globe Ltd. (GLOB)  advanced the most
since Sept. 7 after the real-estate investor was raised to
“buy” from “market perform” at  Leader Capital Markets (LDRC)  Ltd.  The shares gained 5.5 percent to 34.47 shekels at the 4:30
p.m. close in Tel Aviv.  Leader also increased its share-price estimate for the
stock to 45 shekels from 40 shekels.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shoshanna Solomon in Tel Aviv at 
 ssolomon22@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Maedler at 
 cmaedler@bloomberg.net  